y family and I are okay, and I hope you=E2=80=99re okay, too. One big lesso=
n, if you want to get philosophical, is that the lack of local newsgatherin=
g makes disasters like these even more difficult to manage. If you are a me=
dia executive, it=E2=80=99s never been a better time to crack this
local news thing.

=C2=A0

