e favorite topics of conversation. Word in Paris is that the world=E2=80=99=
s most worshiped luxury firm is prepping for the launch of a new category. =
More on that below, plus a couple quick thoughts from me. And if you need a=
 true distraction from the tragedy at hand, might I suggest checking out to=
morrow=E2=80=99s episode of
